						<div class="postbody">CHR-RAM utilization is not too bad right now. Obviously the player is facing some serious fragmentation, but I can deal with that without too much trouble. For 12 unique animation frames, many of them larger than 16x32, I think the utilization of the space is reasonable.<br /><br /><img src="http://i.imgur.com/ecFT0nk.png" alt="Image" /></div>

