					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I really like that sprite. It does stand out in its new environment. So, maybe athletic/acrobatic powerups? That would be cool together with avoiding enemies. Slide through/under stuff, somersault for a different trajectory, stop jump trajectory for a quick fall-down (or up?!), cliff/rope hang and pull up/let go, you can probably come up with a lot within that theme. <br /><br />If just avoiding enemies proves to be too plain (hard to know) in itself but you like it to be a feature somehow, how about that the only weapons you get are sub weapons? One at a time, and/or expendable, or timed. <br /><br />Is there a reason for the two very similiar grays?</div>

					
